    <h2 id="overview">Oil-Based Fluid Purification Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Industrial oil-based fluids — including cutting oils, quench oils, and neat metalworking fluids — degrade over time as they accumulate metal fines, grinding dust, scale, and moisture. A <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc stack centrifuge</a> continuously removes these contaminants, restoring fluid clarity and performance without costly full-batch replacements.
    </p>
    <p>
      Dolphin Centrifuge provides turnkey <a href="/centrifuge-system/">centrifuge systems</a> engineered specifically for oil-based fluid purification. Our systems process 5–30 GPM and handle viscosities typical of straight oils and soluble oil concentrates used across CNC machining, heat treatment, and metal forming operations.
    </p>

